results.name: A triangle related to the GF(z) formulas of the rows of the ED1 array A167546.
comment: The GF(z) formulas given below correspond to the first ten rows of the ED1 array A167546. The polynomials in their numerators lead to the triangle given above.
xref: A000142, A000142 (n=>2) and 120*A062148 (with three extra terms at the beginning of the sequence) equal the first three left hand triangle columns.
A098557(n) and A098557(n)*A064455(n) equal the first two right hand triangle columns.
results.author: _Johannes W. Meijer_, Nov 10 2009
